{"tid":1564088,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《榮光》微調版：只改幾個較突兀沙石位","createTime":"2019-09-12T15:40:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T16:01:54.000Z","uid":269265,"like":9,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7df6e979d4d400716b7cd32bb8029113d3a4d1ff","tid":1564088,"uid":269265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:40:51.000Z","msg":"最近大家對《榮光》歌詞甚多爭論。一派認為歌詞甚多沙石，甚至由此推論香港人文學水平欠佳；另一派則認為歌詞已經深入民心，無謂改來改去。<br />\n<br />\n其實，此詞言淺意深，引人共鳴，晚星一段更富意境，真的無謂大改。最大沙石不外數處：<br />\n<br />\n一、生造詞語：「默沉」、「抗對」<br />\n二、虛字太多：尤其太多「這」字，如「這香港」，累贅，且語調太疏離<br />\n<br />\n至於不句句押韻，則問題不大。詞人似乎有意識地每段最後一句不押韻。可能是為了不過於順口、不似流行曲，這樣反而有種莊重感。<br />\n<br />\n小弟建議只改數處，是為「微調版」。以下改動有些來自小弟，有些參考其他巴絲。歡迎大家繼續修訂。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">《願榮光歸香港》微調版</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">何以這土地　淚再流<br />\n何以令眾人　亦憤恨<br />\n昂首<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">闊步行</span></span>     吶喊聲響透<br />\n盼自由<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">凱歌高奏</span></span><br />\n<br />\n何以這恐懼　抹不走<br />\n何以為信念　從沒退後<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">前方</span></span>血在流　邁進聲響透<br />\n建自由光輝香港<br />\n<br />\n在晚星墜落　徬徨午夜<br />\n迷霧裡　最遠處    吹來號角聲<br />\n捍自由　來齊集這裡　來<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">同步進退</span></span><br />\n勇氣　智慧　也永不滅<br />\n<br />\n黎明來到　要光復    <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我</span></span>香港<br />\n同行兒女　為正義　時代革命<br />\n祈求民主與自由　萬世都不朽<br />\n我願榮光歸香港</span>"},{"pid":"60f6bc86b48eb9e76b59e12f70157e849194d4ba","tid":1564088,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:42:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"a8b6adb5e76fd0e78fa514c707546ff0577afb36","tid":1564088,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:42:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個個都唔知有咩行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />對唔對得住烈士同被捕手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>星期五 <span style=\"color: red;\">獅子山之路</span> 7:30 樂富 <br />\n</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9KQxrNJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9KQxrNJ.png&h=c869dffa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>星期六 <span style=\"color: red;\">天水圍親子遊行</span> 2:30 天秀公園</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O0LtKzJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO0LtKzJ.jpg&h=85f2aac9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>星期日 <span style=\"color: red;\">金鐘民陣遊行</span> 2:30 東角道</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/09/12/185803_2cefd2fa1345b60607d92f6a90928d20.png\" data-thumbn